{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef08063c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1926f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1926f"},"text":"§ 1926f.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Contracts with not-for-profit third parties","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"On and after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2005-11-10"},"text":"November 10, 2005","children":[],"tail":", notwithstanding the provisions of the Consolidated Farm and Rural Development Act ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1921"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 1921","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] (including the associated regulations) governing the Community Facilities Program, the Secretary may allow all Community Facility Program facility borrowers and grantees to enter into contracts with not-for-profit third parties for services consistent with the requirements of the Program, grant, and/or loan: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That the contracts protect the interests of the Government regarding cost, liability, maintenance, and administrative fees."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef08063d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/97/tVII/s756"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–97, title VII, § 756","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2005-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 2005","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/119/2157"},"text":"119 Stat. 2157","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idef08063e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idef08063f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idef080640-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Consolidated Farm and Rural Development Act, referred to in text, is title III of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1961-08-08"},"text":"Aug. 8, 1961","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/75/307"},"text":"75 Stat. 307","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of the Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1921"},"text":"section 1921 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idef080641-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Agriculture, Rural Development, Food and Drug Administration, and Related Agencies Appropriations Act, 2006, and not as part of the Consolidated Farm and Rural Development Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idef080642-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Provisions similar to those in this section were contained in the following prior appropriation acts:","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/447/dA/tVII/s770"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–447, div. A, title VII, § 770","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-12-08"},"text":"Dec. 8, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/2848"},"text":"118 Stat. 2848","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/199/dA/tVII/s775"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–199, div. A, title VII, § 775","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-01-23"},"text":"Jan. 23, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/40"},"text":"118 Stat. 40","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
